title: James O’Connor, Kury Mann and Kieran Harper perform miracle trick shots at underwear shoot | The
text:
Footballers James O’Connor, Kurt Mann and Kieran Harper had no issue flaunting what they’ve got at a recent photo shoot for the Funky Trunks underwear brand — and we’re not talking about their physiques.
The trio hammed it up for the cameras throughout the shoot, showing off their impressive oval ball skills and performing a series of trick shots that look too good to be true.
Check out the video in the player above and judge the skill of the three footballers for yourself .
Originally published as Nude footy stars show off their tricks
